

	 
      "BRANDY, n.  A cordial composed of one part thunder-and-lightning, one  part remorse, two parts bloody murder, one part death-hell-and-the-  grave and four parts clarified Satan.  Dose, a headful all the time.   Brandy is said by Dr. Johnson to be the drink of heroes.  Only a hero  will venture to drink it." quote from Ambrose Bierce
    
